query:
SELECT h.id, h.name, h.linkedDocumentId, d.id as doc_id, d.fileName, d.fileUrl 
FROM hotels h 
LEFT JOIN documents d ON h.linkedDocumentId = d.id 
WHERE h.name LIKE '%Vienna%parking%' OR h.name LIKE '%parking%Vienna%';
